{"title":"押注运气玄学：基于三角洲烽火杯的押注运气研究","slug":"押注运气玄学：基于三角洲烽火杯的押注运气研究","date":"2026-04-17T16:05:41.363Z","updated":"2026-04-18T07:56:34.920Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/押注运气玄学：基于三角洲烽火杯的押注运气研究.json","excerpt":"**摘要**   本研究以三角洲烽火杯赛事为背景，通过分析作者连续11场押注三支队伍的名次数据，探讨其“运气差”的主观感受是否具有统计学依据。结果显示，押注队伍的平均排名（3.67）略高于随机期望（3.5），晋级成功率（72.7%）也低于理论值（80%），但差异未达显著性水平。结合认知心理学分析发现，主观上的“运气差”是客观劣势与负性偏误共同作用的结果：人类对失败的敏感度更高、期望与现实落差放大负面体验，以及极端名次（如第5、6名）的频繁出现强化了“选错队”的印象。尽管数据未证实“极度倒霉”，但建议调整心理预期或优化押注策略以提升参与感。","covers":null,"content":"<!-- 这是一个用于发布新论文的模板，如要发布通讯、新闻，删除这些默认内容即可。 -->\n<p>Leaf<sup>1,*</sup><br>\n<sup>1</sup>Beijing Normal University<br>\n<sup>*</sup><a href=\"mailto:2461743456@qq.com\">2461743456@qq.com</a></p>\n<!-- 以下请在href=后的双引号里填写pdf全网链接 -->\n<a href=\"https://file.rubbish.press/artical/%E6%8A%BC%E6%B3%A8%E8%BF%90%E6%B0%94%E7%8E%84%E5%AD%A6%EF%BC%9A%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%89%E8%A7%92%E6%B4%B2%E7%83%BD%E7%81%AB%E6%9D%AF%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%BC%E6%B3%A8%E8%BF%90%E6%B0%94%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6.pdf?preview\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 10px 18px; background: #2563eb; color: white; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; transition: all 0.2s;\">\n  <svg style=\"width:18px;height:18px;fill:currentColor;\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n    <path d=\"M20 2H8c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h12c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V4c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 14H8V4h12v12zM4 6H2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14v-2H4V6zm12 6V9l-4 4-4-4v3h8z\"/>\n  </svg>\n  阅读 PDF 全文\n</a>\n<hr>\n<h1>摘要</h1>\n<p>本研究以三角洲烽火杯赛事为背景，收集了笔者连续十一场比赛中每场押注三支队伍的名次数据，旨在检验其“运气差”的主观感受是否具有统计学依据。结果表明，押注队伍的平均排名显著高于理论随机期望，晋级成功率低于理论值，但差异尚未达到极端显著性。结合认知心理学，本文认为“运气差”在一定程度上是客观劣势与主观负性偏误共同作用的结果。</p>\n<p><strong>关键词</strong>:三角洲;运气玄学;晋级概率;认知偏误</p>\n<h1>1 引言</h1>\n<p>笔者最近忙于写本科毕业论文，实在不想写的时候就看一看游戏比赛直播。在三角洲烽火杯赛制下，每场六队角逐，前两名晋级。笔者在每场比赛前通过“押注”三支队伍来增加参与感(注:不包含任何金钱交易，纯属思想预期)。然而，笔者在观赛期间常常感觉自己运气奇差无比，押的队伍总是赢不了。明明该队伍之前表现一直很好，但笔者一看好他们，他们就成绩一般。这激起了笔者的思考。</p>\n<p>本文试图回答以下问题:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>押注队伍的名次分布是否显著劣于随机预期?</li>\n<li>主观感受“运气差”是源于真实劣势，还是认知偏误?</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"2-研究方法\">2 研究方法</h2>\n<h3 id=\"2-1-数据来源\">2.1 数据来源</h3>\n<p>笔者于十一场比赛中记录了每场押注的三支队伍最终名次(1至6名，1为最优，6为最劣)。数据整理如下表:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>场次</th>\n<th>名次1</th>\n<th>名次2</th>\n<th>名次3</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>11</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>6</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"2-2-分析指标\">2.2 分析指标</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>平均排名</strong>:三支队伍名次的均值。</li>\n<li><strong>晋级成功率</strong>:每场是否有至少一支队伍进入前两名(即名次1或2)。</li>\n<li><strong>理论随机期望</strong>:在完全随机情况下，从6支队伍中任选3支，平均排名的期望值为 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow><mn>6</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>3.5</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\frac{1+2+3+4+5+6}{6}=3.5</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.1901em;vertical-align:-0.345em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8451em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.655em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">6</span></span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.394em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">1</span><span class=\"mbin mtight\">+</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span><span class=\"mbin mtight\">+</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">3</span><span class=\"mbin mtight\">+</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">4</span><span class=\"mbin mtight\">+</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">5</span><span class=\"mbin mtight\">+</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">6</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.345em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3.5</span></span></span></span>，期望晋级概率为$ 1-\\frac{c_4^3}{c_6^3}=1-\\frac{4}{20}$ 即80%的场次至少有一支晋级)。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"3-数据分析结果\">3 数据分析结果</h2>\n<h3 id=\"3-1-平均排名分析\">3.1 平均排名分析</h3>\n<p>十一场押注队伍的平均排名如下:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>场次</th>\n<th>平均排名</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>3.33</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>3.67</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>3.67</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>3.67</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>4.67</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>4.00</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>3.00</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>4.00</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9</td>\n<td>2.67</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10</td>\n<td>3.00</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>11</td>\n<td>4.67</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>总体平均排名 = <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>3.33</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>3.67</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>3.67</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>3.67</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>4.67</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>4.00</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>3.00</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>4.00</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>2.67</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>3.00</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>4.67</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mn>11</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>3.67</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">(3.33+3.67+3.67+3.67+4.67+4.00+3.00+4.00+2.67+3.00+4.67)/11=3.67</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">3.33</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3.67</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3.67</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3.67</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">4.67</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">4.00</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3.00</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">4.00</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2.67</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3.00</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">4.67</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mord\">/11</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3.67</span></span></span></span>。</p>\n<p>理论随机期望平均排名 = 3.50</p>\n<p>实际平均排名 = 3.67，高于期望值(数值越大排名越差)，表明押注队伍整体成绩略劣于随机选择。</p>\n<h3 id=\"3-2-晋级成功率分析\">3.2 晋级成功率分析</h3>\n<p>在十一场中，至少有一支押注队伍进入前两名的场次为:第1、2、3、4、7、8、9、10场，共8场。</p>\n<p>晋级成功率 =$ 8/11 \\approx 72.7%$。</p>\n<p>理论随机期望 = 80%，实际成功率低于期望7.3个百分点。</p>\n<h3 id=\"3-3-显著性检验\">3.3 显著性检验</h3>\n<p>采用单样本t检验(平均排名 vs 3.5)，得 t=0.65，p=0.53&gt;0.05，未达到统计学显著水平。</p>\n<p>晋级成功率采用二项检验，在期望80%下，11场中成功$ 8$场的单侧概率 $ P(X \\leq 8) \\approx 0.38$,同样不显著。</p>\n<h2 id=\"4-结果与讨论\">4 结果与讨论</h2>\n<h3 id=\"4-1-“运气差”的真实成分\">4.1 “运气差”的真实成分</h3>\n<p>从数据上看，押注队伍的平均排名($ 3.67<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mtext>确实劣于随机预期</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">)确实劣于随机预期(</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">确实劣于随机预期</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span></span></span></span> 3.50<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mtext>，晋级成功率</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">)，晋级成功率(</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">，晋级成功率</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span></span></span></span> 72.7%<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mtext>也低于理论值</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">)也低于理论值(</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">也低于理论值</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span></span></span></span> 80%$)。因此，“成绩普遍较差&quot;并非纯粹的错觉，而是存在一定程度的真实劣势。</p>\n<p>然而，这种差异在统计学上并不显著，意味着若长期重复，结果可能趋近于随机水平。当前表现虽不理想，但并未达到“极端倒霉”的程度。</p>\n<h3 id=\"4-2-为何主观感受远强于客观数据\">4.2 为何主观感受远强于客观数据?</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>负性偏误</strong>:人类对失败和失望的记忆远强于成功。当押注队伍排名靠后时(如多次出现第5、6名)，其情感冲击会覆盖掉偶尔的晋级喜悦。</li>\n<li><strong>期望与现实的落差</strong>:押注三支队伍，理论上晋级概率高达$ 80%<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>，这意味着“未晋级”是小概率事件。当小概率事件在</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">，这意味着“未晋级”是小概率事件。当小概率事件在</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">，这意味着</span><span class=\"mord\">“</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">未晋级</span><span class=\"mord\">”</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">是小概率事件。当小概率事件在</span></span></span></span> 11<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>场中发生</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">场中发生</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">场中发生</span></span></span></span> 3<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>次</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mtext>约</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">次(约</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">次</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">约</span></span></span></span> 27%$)，会感觉“连这么高概率都翻车”，从而强化“运气差”的认知。</li>\n<li><strong>名次分布的非对称性</strong>:即便有队伍晋级，另外两支队伍若长期排名末尾(如第5、6名),也会给人“整体不行”的感觉。数据中，第 $ 5<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>、</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">、</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">、</span></span></span></span> 6<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>名共出现</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">名共出现</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">名共出现</span></span></span></span> 13<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>次</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mtext>占比</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">次(占比</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">次</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">占比</span></span></span></span> 39%<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mtext>，显著高于随机期望的</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">)，显著高于随机期望的</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">，显著高于随机期望的</span></span></span></span> 33%$，进一步加深了“押中坑队”的印象。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"4-3-理论意义与局限性\">4.3 理论意义与局限性</h3>\n<p>本研究首次将“押运玄学”纳入量化分析，揭示了主观感受与客观数据之间的微妙关系。但研究存在局限:样本量较小(仅<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>11</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">11</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">11</span></span></span></span>场)，未考虑队伍实力差异、场次间相关性等因素。未来可采用更长时间的追踪,并结合队伍实力模型，进一步区分“运气”与“选队策略问题”。</p>\n<h2 id=\"5-结论\">5 结论</h2>\n<p>本研究表明，笔者的“运气差”并非纯粹错觉,押注队伍的平均排名略劣于随机水平,晋级成功率也低于理论值。但由于差异未达统计学显著，实际并未陷入“极度倒霉”的境地。主观上强烈的“运气差”感受，更多源于认知偏误与少数极端名次带来的负面强化。</p>\n<p>对有同样困惑的人建议:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>若追求晋级体验，可考虑选择赛前实力评估靠前的队伍，而非完全凭直觉。</li>\n<li>调整心理预期:<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>80</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">%</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">80\\%</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8056em;vertical-align:-0.0556em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">80%</span></span></span></span>的晋级概率意味着每五场就会有一场全军覆没，属于正常波动。</li>\n<li>若仍感痛苦，可尝试减少押注队伍数量，降低期望管理成本。</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"声明\">声明</h2>\n<p>本文与三角洲行动官方无关，纯属自娱自乐。</p>\n<h2 id=\"致谢\">致谢</h2>\n<p>感谢三角洲烽火职业联赛，本科毕业论文写不下去了我就看比赛，看着看着就忘记写论文了。哈哈。</p>\n<h2 id=\"参考文献\">参考文献</h2>\n<p>本文无需任何参考文献(doge)</p>\n","more":"<!-- 这是一个用于发布新论文的模板，如要发布通讯、新闻，删除这些默认内容即可。 -->\n<p>Leaf<sup>1,*</sup><br>\n<sup>1</sup>Beijing Normal University<br>\n<sup>*</sup><a href=\"mailto:2461743456@qq.com\">2461743456@qq.com</a></p>\n<!-- 以下请在href=后的双引号里填写pdf全网链接 -->\n<a href=\"https://file.rubbish.press/artical/%E6%8A%BC%E6%B3%A8%E8%BF%90%E6%B0%94%E7%8E%84%E5%AD%A6%EF%BC%9A%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%89%E8%A7%92%E6%B4%B2%E7%83%BD%E7%81%AB%E6%9D%AF%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%BC%E6%B3%A8%E8%BF%90%E6%B0%94%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6.pdf?preview\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 10px 18px; background: #2563eb; color: white; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; transition: all 0.2s;\">\n  <svg style=\"width:18px;height:18px;fill:currentColor;\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n    <path d=\"M20 2H8c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h12c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V4c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 14H8V4h12v12zM4 6H2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14v-2H4V6zm12 6V9l-4 4-4-4v3h8z\"/>\n  </svg>\n  阅读 PDF 全文\n</a>\n<hr>\n<h1>摘要</h1>\n<p>本研究以三角洲烽火杯赛事为背景，收集了笔者连续十一场比赛中每场押注三支队伍的名次数据，旨在检验其“运气差”的主观感受是否具有统计学依据。结果表明，押注队伍的平均排名显著高于理论随机期望，晋级成功率低于理论值，但差异尚未达到极端显著性。结合认知心理学，本文认为“运气差”在一定程度上是客观劣势与主观负性偏误共同作用的结果。</p>\n<p><strong>关键词</strong>:三角洲;运气玄学;晋级概率;认知偏误</p>\n<h1>1 引言</h1>\n<p>笔者最近忙于写本科毕业论文，实在不想写的时候就看一看游戏比赛直播。在三角洲烽火杯赛制下，每场六队角逐，前两名晋级。笔者在每场比赛前通过“押注”三支队伍来增加参与感(注:不包含任何金钱交易，纯属思想预期)。然而，笔者在观赛期间常常感觉自己运气奇差无比，押的队伍总是赢不了。明明该队伍之前表现一直很好，但笔者一看好他们，他们就成绩一般。这激起了笔者的思考。</p>\n<p>本文试图回答以下问题:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>押注队伍的名次分布是否显著劣于随机预期?</li>\n<li>主观感受“运气差”是源于真实劣势，还是认知偏误?</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"2-研究方法\">2 研究方法</h2>\n<h3 id=\"2-1-数据来源\">2.1 数据来源</h3>\n<p>笔者于十一场比赛中记录了每场押注的三支队伍最终名次(1至6名，1为最优，6为最劣)。数据整理如下表:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>场次</th>\n<th>名次1</th>\n<th>名次2</th>\n<th>名次3</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>11</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>6</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"2-2-分析指标\">2.2 分析指标</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>平均排名</strong>:三支队伍名次的均值。</li>\n<li><strong>晋级成功率</strong>:每场是否有至少一支队伍进入前两名(即名次1或2)。</li>\n<li><strong>理论随机期望</strong>:在完全随机情况下，从6支队伍中任选3支，平均排名的期望值为 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow><mn>6</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>3.5</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\frac{1+2+3+4+5+6}{6}=3.5</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.1901em;vertical-align:-0.345em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8451em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.655em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">6</span></span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.394em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">1</span><span class=\"mbin mtight\">+</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span><span class=\"mbin mtight\">+</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">3</span><span class=\"mbin mtight\">+</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">4</span><span class=\"mbin mtight\">+</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">5</span><span class=\"mbin mtight\">+</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">6</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.345em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3.5</span></span></span></span>，期望晋级概率为$ 1-\\frac{c_4^3}{c_6^3}=1-\\frac{4}{20}$ 即80%的场次至少有一支晋级)。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"3-数据分析结果\">3 数据分析结果</h2>\n<h3 id=\"3-1-平均排名分析\">3.1 平均排名分析</h3>\n<p>十一场押注队伍的平均排名如下:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>场次</th>\n<th>平均排名</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>3.33</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>3.67</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>3.67</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>3.67</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>4.67</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>4.00</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>3.00</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>4.00</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9</td>\n<td>2.67</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10</td>\n<td>3.00</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>11</td>\n<td>4.67</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>总体平均排名 = <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>3.33</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>3.67</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>3.67</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>3.67</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>4.67</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>4.00</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>3.00</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>4.00</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>2.67</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>3.00</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>4.67</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mn>11</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>3.67</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">(3.33+3.67+3.67+3.67+4.67+4.00+3.00+4.00+2.67+3.00+4.67)/11=3.67</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">3.33</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3.67</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3.67</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3.67</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">4.67</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">4.00</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3.00</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">4.00</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2.67</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3.00</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">4.67</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mord\">/11</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3.67</span></span></span></span>。</p>\n<p>理论随机期望平均排名 = 3.50</p>\n<p>实际平均排名 = 3.67，高于期望值(数值越大排名越差)，表明押注队伍整体成绩略劣于随机选择。</p>\n<h3 id=\"3-2-晋级成功率分析\">3.2 晋级成功率分析</h3>\n<p>在十一场中，至少有一支押注队伍进入前两名的场次为:第1、2、3、4、7、8、9、10场，共8场。</p>\n<p>晋级成功率 =$ 8/11 \\approx 72.7%$。</p>\n<p>理论随机期望 = 80%，实际成功率低于期望7.3个百分点。</p>\n<h3 id=\"3-3-显著性检验\">3.3 显著性检验</h3>\n<p>采用单样本t检验(平均排名 vs 3.5)，得 t=0.65，p=0.53&gt;0.05，未达到统计学显著水平。</p>\n<p>晋级成功率采用二项检验，在期望80%下，11场中成功$ 8$场的单侧概率 $ P(X \\leq 8) \\approx 0.38$,同样不显著。</p>\n<h2 id=\"4-结果与讨论\">4 结果与讨论</h2>\n<h3 id=\"4-1-“运气差”的真实成分\">4.1 “运气差”的真实成分</h3>\n<p>从数据上看，押注队伍的平均排名($ 3.67<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mtext>确实劣于随机预期</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">)确实劣于随机预期(</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">确实劣于随机预期</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span></span></span></span> 3.50<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mtext>，晋级成功率</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">)，晋级成功率(</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">，晋级成功率</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span></span></span></span> 72.7%<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mtext>也低于理论值</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">)也低于理论值(</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">也低于理论值</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span></span></span></span> 80%$)。因此，“成绩普遍较差&quot;并非纯粹的错觉，而是存在一定程度的真实劣势。</p>\n<p>然而，这种差异在统计学上并不显著，意味着若长期重复，结果可能趋近于随机水平。当前表现虽不理想，但并未达到“极端倒霉”的程度。</p>\n<h3 id=\"4-2-为何主观感受远强于客观数据\">4.2 为何主观感受远强于客观数据?</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>负性偏误</strong>:人类对失败和失望的记忆远强于成功。当押注队伍排名靠后时(如多次出现第5、6名)，其情感冲击会覆盖掉偶尔的晋级喜悦。</li>\n<li><strong>期望与现实的落差</strong>:押注三支队伍，理论上晋级概率高达$ 80%<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>，这意味着“未晋级”是小概率事件。当小概率事件在</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">，这意味着“未晋级”是小概率事件。当小概率事件在</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">，这意味着</span><span class=\"mord\">“</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">未晋级</span><span class=\"mord\">”</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">是小概率事件。当小概率事件在</span></span></span></span> 11<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>场中发生</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">场中发生</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">场中发生</span></span></span></span> 3<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>次</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mtext>约</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">次(约</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">次</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">约</span></span></span></span> 27%$)，会感觉“连这么高概率都翻车”，从而强化“运气差”的认知。</li>\n<li><strong>名次分布的非对称性</strong>:即便有队伍晋级，另外两支队伍若长期排名末尾(如第5、6名),也会给人“整体不行”的感觉。数据中，第 $ 5<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>、</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">、</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">、</span></span></span></span> 6<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>名共出现</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">名共出现</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">名共出现</span></span></span></span> 13<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>次</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mtext>占比</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">次(占比</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">次</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">占比</span></span></span></span> 39%<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mtext>，显著高于随机期望的</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">)，显著高于随机期望的</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">，显著高于随机期望的</span></span></span></span> 33%$，进一步加深了“押中坑队”的印象。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"4-3-理论意义与局限性\">4.3 理论意义与局限性</h3>\n<p>本研究首次将“押运玄学”纳入量化分析，揭示了主观感受与客观数据之间的微妙关系。但研究存在局限:样本量较小(仅<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>11</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">11</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">11</span></span></span></span>场)，未考虑队伍实力差异、场次间相关性等因素。未来可采用更长时间的追踪,并结合队伍实力模型，进一步区分“运气”与“选队策略问题”。</p>\n<h2 id=\"5-结论\">5 结论</h2>\n<p>本研究表明，笔者的“运气差”并非纯粹错觉,押注队伍的平均排名略劣于随机水平,晋级成功率也低于理论值。但由于差异未达统计学显著，实际并未陷入“极度倒霉”的境地。主观上强烈的“运气差”感受，更多源于认知偏误与少数极端名次带来的负面强化。</p>\n<p>对有同样困惑的人建议:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>若追求晋级体验，可考虑选择赛前实力评估靠前的队伍，而非完全凭直觉。</li>\n<li>调整心理预期:<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>80</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">%</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">80\\%</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8056em;vertical-align:-0.0556em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">80%</span></span></span></span>的晋级概率意味着每五场就会有一场全军覆没，属于正常波动。</li>\n<li>若仍感痛苦，可尝试减少押注队伍数量，降低期望管理成本。</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"声明\">声明</h2>\n<p>本文与三角洲行动官方无关，纯属自娱自乐。</p>\n<h2 id=\"致谢\">致谢</h2>\n<p>感谢三角洲烽火职业联赛，本科毕业论文写不下去了我就看比赛，看着看着就忘记写论文了。哈哈。</p>\n<h2 id=\"参考文献\">参考文献</h2>\n<p>本文无需任何参考文献(doge)</p>\n","categories":[{"name":"文章","path":"api/categories/文章.json"},{"name":"实用","path":"api/categories/实用.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"三角洲","path":"api/tags/三角洲.json"},{"name":"运气玄学","path":"api/tags/运气玄学.json"},{"name":"晋级概率","path":"api/tags/晋级概率.json"},{"name":"认知偏误","path":"api/tags/认知偏误.json"}]}